metadata.name: The Wizards Lair
metadata.description:
The wizards lair is a small, round hut made entirely of mushrooms. It has a small door and a window, and is surrounded by a ring of toadstools. It is said that this hut is inhabited by a wizard who is able to grant wishes to those who are worthy. Its said that other animals that live close by come to visit the wizard. These animals are all very friendly and love to play with the wizard's children. 

  

768 x 1024p 

1/1
